Ford:
->gave assembly lines big breakthrough
->1.5 crores car
->50% of world car producion 100 years back
->Model T- Car of the millenium.
->All work fragmentation,tasks related to cars were owned completely by ford.
->couldn't offer variety
Toyota:
->nowhere compared to Ford
->next biggest change in supply chain
->made suppliers to move nearby
->1950-1980:We'll manufacture engine and gear box and also do assembly
